screen shots of android application. this commercial android application has php,MySQL and remote database as its backend.
The google firebase is used to authenticate the user via otp. Farmer can upload their products, its price and quantity.
The user see the price and if they interest to buy the product from seller the can directly call the seller by click the call button.
This is same as farmer to seed sellers.
Admin app is used to monitor the what happen in the efarmer market. via admin app admin can see who are sell the product and what they sell 
and can get the full detail of seller in admin application.
